The Crop Water Stress Index (CWSI) is a reasonable quantitative evaluation parameter for crop water stress under evaporation pressure loss [109–111]. The CWSI can be calculated by the formula follows:1CWSI=Tc-Ta-Tc-TallTc-Taul-Tc-Tall\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
